Rules
-Class cannot start with digit
-class cannot be a java keyword
-no spaces


Traditions
-Class name start with uppercase letter 
"MyFirstJavaProgran"  < is  a example.
-Filename must the same with the class name



How to Run Java Program?
-Always complied the program after add or update.
方法是 在command line 輸入 javac 檔名.java
接者在 正常的 java 檔名 
以上兩步驟即可 

Change Directory 很重要
方法 - cd 檔名
回上一層 cd .. 
以上兩步驟即可

1/30 Loop

1. Enhanced for loop: When you need to visit each element in an array.
2. For loop: use it on thing that require counting, or run a block of code for the times I want (Arrays)
3. While loop: Reading text file, open-ended jobs, you dont know how many times inside the file.

2/11
1. 當我們在設計for loop的條件時 i=0 這代表從最開始的第一個開始 i<5 代表者 當她碰到執行到第五次時候 就停止 i++ 代表 每一次執行 i+1

 for (int i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
        if (i % 2 == 0) {
            g.setColor(Color.RED); // Odd number draw red
        } else {
            g.setColor(Color.WHITE); // even number draw white
        }
        g.fillRect(0, i*h1, w1, h1); // the position and width and hight of the flag
   }
